     F                                              KINFSR *PSSR
     FAM#WP64 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAM#PP51 O   E                    DISK                      A
      *
     E                    ER      1  11 65
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   8 S1SHID
     I                                        2   3 S1TRKB
     I                                        5   7 S1IAFB
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140W4PST
     I                                        1   80W4PSTD
     I                                        9  140W4PSTT
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140W4PED
     I                                        1   80W4PEDD
     I                                        9  140W4PEDT
